A component has 4 files

For example Display Component
------------------------------
    - display.component.ts
    - display.component.html
    - display.component.css
    - display.component.spec.ts

Steps to create a component
-----------------------------
2 ways to create

1st Way
--------
    - manually create all the above specified files.
    - make an entry of the component in app.module.ts file.
    - Don't forget to use the selector of the component.

2nd Way
--------
    - Use the command
        ng generate component display
            (or)
        ng g c display
    - Since we use the command no need to make an entry in the app.module.ts file.
        It is automatically done.
    - Don't forget to use the selector of the component.